Serendio,helps,companies,transform,multi,structured,data,into,insight,and,decisions,through,the,use,of,big,data,text,analytics,machine,learning,and,predictive,science,Serendio,s,APIs,allow,developers,to,tap,into,unstructured,content,to,tag,and,extract,entities,find,relationships,between,entities,discover,sentiments,identify,topics,and,classify,topics,These,APIs,are,implemented,using,a,RESTful,interface,with,calls,formatted,for,either,XML,or,JSON,responses